V0103_01_00_00_1.text: You're just choosing the method of your defeat!

V0103_01_00_01_1.text: And it's destiny that my heroes will guide me to victory!

V0103_01_00_02_0.text: I'll show you what a Deck of REAL heroes can do!

V0103_03_00_00_0.text: You've got a lot to learn about destiny, and I'm controlling yours!

V0103_03_00_01_0.text:
Hmm, your strategy is interesting.
I said "interesting", not "good"!

V0103_03_00_02_0.text: My Destiny HEROES are far superior to the Elemental HEROES!

V0103_03_00_03_0.text: You'll see why I'm a pro!

V0103_03_00_05_0.text: I still believe in every Destiny HERO that my dad designed!

V0103_13_00_00_0.text: I'll end your destiny with the life force of all things!

Here comes my new pal!
Destiny HERO - Diamond Dude!

You're in for double the trouble!
Destiny HERO - Double Dude!

V0103_13_00_06_0.text: Destiny HERO - Dunker's coming to slam you down!

V0103_13_00_08_0.text: Destiny HERO - Disk Commander, come on out!

V0103_13_00_14_1.text: Come on out, Destiny HERO - Dreadmaster!

V0103_13_00_15_0.text: Destiny HERO - Dread Servant has arrived!

V0103_13_00_17_0.text: Check out my Elemental HERO Phoenix Enforcer!

V0103_13_00_20_1.text: Show yourself, Destiny HERO - Dark Angel!

V0103_13_00_28_0.text: I present to you, Destiny HERO - Decider!

V0103_19_00_07_0.text: Malicious! Show no mercy and attack!

V0103_19_00_15_0.text: Destiny HERO - Dread Servant, send 'em out with a bang!

V0103_19_00_22_0.text: Show 'em what you got, Vyon! Attack!

V0103_19_00_28_0.text: Decider! Attack and determine my opponent's fate!

V0103_28_00_00_0.text: Fate has already chosen me to be the best.

V0103_28_00_01_0.text: Winning Duels is a piece 'a cake when destiny’s got your back!

V0103_28_00_02_0.text: I can tell that you doubted yourself.

V0103_28_00_02_1.text: If you don't believe in your moves, you can never become a true Duelist.

V0103_28_00_03_0.text: Did you honestly believe there are heroes greater than my Destiny HEROES?

V0103_28_00_04_0.text:
You have the skills of a baby.
Go home and cry in your Ojama pajamas.

V0103_28_00_07_0.text: I gotta say, Zaney. I thought you'd be tougher.

V0103_28_00_07_1.text: If you can't keep your cool, your pro career is over before it's started.

V0103_29_00_00_0.text:
My Destiny HEROES were defeated...
Forgive me, Dad.

V0103_29_00_01_0.text:
How? How could I have lost?
I didn't make a single mistake!

V0103_29_00_02_1.text: Just a minor setback on my way to becoming the champ in the pro leagues!

V0103_29_00_03_0.text: I may have lost, but it's not because your Elemental HEROES are greater than my Destiny HEROES!

V0103_29_00_03_1.text: I just made a few mistakes, zigging when I shoulda been zagging.

V0103_29_00_04_1.text: We'll have our rematch on the pro circuit!

V0103_30_00_01_0.text: I'm not even breaking a sweat.

V0103_33_00_00_0.text: You're about to find out why I'm a pro and you're an amateur!

V0103_34_00_00_0.text: No one can stop the hands of fate!

V0103_34_00_01_0.text: You'll never know what it takes to be a true hero like me!

V0103_34_00_02_0.text: Destiny HEROES control the fate of the future!

V0103_34_00_04_0.text: A pro never accidentally reveals his best strategies.

V0103_34_00_06_0.text: Against a pro Duelist like me, you're way out of your league!

V0103_35_00_00_0.text: You'll learn what it takes to be a pro.

V0103_27_00_02_0.text: I'm just giving you a handicap!
